Rema – Rema’s Realm (Episode One) Mavin Records superstar, Rema is arguably Nigeria’s hottest wonder kid at the moment, he has done a lot in the music industry under a year of introduction. However, the boy gone further to prove that he’s not just a talented singer, but also a good actor. The multi-talented singer serves a new short film which he tagged “Rema’s Realm” featuring his partner in crime, his fellow commando, London. SEE ALSO: Rema – Bad Commando Rema has this so say: Hey I’m Rema, I know you might be wondering what’s about to happen next but me and my friends are about to take the worst decisions of our life, why? because In these streets there’s no love and we’re exposed to bad influence. The video was shot and directed by Ademola Falomo. Check it out and share your thoughts below. STREAM BAD COMMANDO EP .notjustok-artist-card-embed {
